  </xml><p class="MsoNormalM"><b>Day 1: Pick-up you from Manali Mall Road , Near manali
Bus stand at 09:00 am Drive from Manali to Gulaba Road head (24 km) (01 Hours’
Drive same Day trek Rola kholi base Camp&nbsp;</b></p>

<p class="MsoNormalM"><b>Total distance –&nbsp;</b>25 km – 2/3 Hours journey</p>

<p class="MsoNormalM">&nbsp;<b>Mode of journey –&nbsp;</b>By taxi 22 km – On foot
06 km</p>

<p class="MsoNormalM">&nbsp;<b>Altitude -Rola Kholi&nbsp;</b>&nbsp;– 12,590 feet</p>

<p class="MsoNormalM">&nbsp;<b>Night stay –&nbsp;</b>Our Camp site – on twin share
basis</p>

<p class="MsoNormalM"><b>9:00 AM: Pick-Up from Manali</b></p>

<ul type="discd">
 <li><b>Location:</b>&nbsp;Manali
     Mall Road, near the Manali Bus Stand.</li>
 <li><b>Note:</b>&nbsp;Ensure
     you’re at the meeting point a few minutes early to avoid any delays.</li>
</ul>

<p class="MsoNormalM"><b>9:15 AM: Departure from Manali</b></p>

<ul type="discd">
 <li><b>Travel
     Mode:</b>&nbsp;Private vehicle (taxi or jeep).</li>
 <li><b>Distance:</b>&nbsp;24
     km</li>
 <li><b>Estimated
     Travel Time:</b>&nbsp;1 hour</li>
</ul>

<p class="MsoNormalM"><b>10:15 AM: Arrival at Gulaba Road Head</b></p>

<ul type="discd">
 <li><b>Description:</b>&nbsp;The
     starting point for your trek. You’ll enjoy beautiful views of the
     surrounding hills and valleys as you prepare for your trek.</li>
</ul>

<p class="MsoNormalM"><b>10:30 AM: Begin Trek to Rola Kholi Base Camp</b></p>

<ul type="discd">
 <li><b>Trek
     Distance:</b>&nbsp;6 km</li>
 <li><b>Altitude:</b>&nbsp;Rola
     Kholi Base Camp is situated at an altitude of approximately 3,200 meters
     (10,500 feet).</li>
 <li><b>Trek
     Duration:</b>&nbsp;Approximately 4-5 hours, depending on your pace.</li>
</ul>

<p class="MsoNormalM"><b>Trek Highlights:</b></p>

<ul type="discd">
 <li><b>Scenery:</b>&nbsp;The
     trail is surrounded by lush green forests, scenic meadows, and stunning
     views of the snow-capped mountains. You may spot various flora and fauna
     along the way.</li>
 <li><b>Breaks:</b>&nbsp;Plan
     to take short breaks for hydration and snacks, allowing you to enjoy the
     surroundings.</li>
</ul>

<p class="MsoNormalM"><b>2:30 PM: Arrival at Rola Kholi Base Camp</b></p>

<ul type="discd">
 <li><b>Settle
     In:</b>&nbsp;Once you arrive at the base camp, you can set up your tents
     or find a comfortable spot to relax.</li>
 <li><b>Lunch:</b>&nbsp;Enjoy
     a packed lunch or snacks at the campsite.</li>
</ul>

<p class="MsoNormalM"><b>Afternoon Activities:</b></p>

<ul type="discd">
 <li><b>Exploration:</b>&nbsp;Take
     a short walk around the camp to enjoy the views or relax and unwind.</li>
 <li><b>Photography:</b>&nbsp;Capture
     the breathtaking scenery and the tranquility of the mountains.</li>
</ul>

<p class="MsoNormalM"><b>Evening:</b></p>

<ul type="discd">
 <li><b>Dinner
     Preparation:</b>&nbsp;Enjoy a hot meal prepared by your guides.</li>
 <li><b>Campfire:</b>&nbsp;If
     conditions allow, gather around a campfire to share stories and enjoy the
     mountain ambiance.</li>
</ul>

<p class="MsoNormalM"><b>Overnight Stay:</b></p>

<ul type="discd">
 <li><b>Accommodation:</b>&nbsp;Tents
     at Rola Kholi Base Camp.</li>
 <li><b>Note:</b>&nbsp;Be
     sure to stay warm and cozy in your sleeping bag, as temperatures can drop
     significantly at night.</li>
</ul>

<p class="MsoNormalM"><b>Important Tips:</b></p>

<ul type="discd">
 <li><b>Gear:</b>&nbsp;Ensure
     you have proper trekking gear, including sturdy shoes, warm clothing, and
     rain gear, if necessary.</li>
 <li><b>Hydration:</b>&nbsp;Carry
     enough water and stay hydrated throughout the day.</li>
 <li><b>Safety:</b>&nbsp;Follow
     your guide’s instructions and stay on marked trails for your safety.</li>
</ul>

<p class="MsoNormalM">This itinerary provides a structured plan for your first
day, ensuring a smooth start to your trekking adventure! If you need more
details or adjustments, feel free to ask.</p></p>                           </div>
